Global Bicycle Mudguard Market Insights
Bicycle Mudguard Market size was valued at USD 0.89 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.56 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Bicycle Mudguard Market Overview
The global bicycle mudguard market is valued at approximately USD 500 million in 2024 and is expected to grow steadily, reaching a market size of USD 700 million by 2030. This growth is driven by the rising popularity of cycling as a sport and a means of transportation, especially in urban areas. The increasing demand for durable and efficient bicycle accessories, like mudguards, is contributing to this market expansion. Mudguards protect cyclists from mud, water, and debris, offering a more comfortable ride, which in turn drives their demand across both recreational and professional cycling sectors. Factors such as product innovation, design improvements, and advancements in materials are further influencing the market growth positively.

